      "question": "What does \u2018working software\u2019 progress mean in agile?",
      "correctAnswer": "Delivered increments that provide real user value\u2014not only documents or plans.",
      "incorrectAnswers": [
        "PowerPoint decks only.",
        "Meeting minutes only.",
        "Architecture diagrams only."
      ],
      "explanation": "Tangible progress reduces risk.",
